 <pb n="1" id="Tw01maid1">  
<div1 type="letter"> 
<opener> 
<seg> 
<figure entity="Tw01maid"> 
<figDesc>Papers of Mark Twain, AN (1901-1903);  
Mark Twain, Riverdale, NY, to Unknown;  
image of page one of the manuscript. 
</figDesc> 
</figure> 
</seg> 
 
<dateline> 
<name type="place"><hi rend="typeset">Riverdale <lb> 
on the Hudson</hi>, New York City &mdash;</name><lb> 
 
<date>Tuesday morning</date></dateline> 
 
</opener> 
 
<p>The bearer is my daughter's <lb> 
maid, &amp; I beg as a favor <lb> 
that you will allow her to <lb> 
have access to my daughter's <lb> 
room, so that she can <lb> 
unpack the trunk. </p> 
 
<closer> 
<salute> Yours very truly </salute> 
<signed>Mark Twain <lb> 
(SL. <hi rend="underline">Clemens</hi>)</signed> 
 
<seg type="postscript">My daughter <lb> 
is Miss Clara <lb> 
Clemens.</seg> 
 
</closer> 
</div1> 
   
